QuestData.Title: Where They Hide
QuestData.Description:
The naga are sending assassins to eliminate our forces.
They hide nearby and murder those they cannot steal away to the slave pens.
Take this special sea sponge with you. The spores will reveal the naga in all their treachery.
Once revealed, slay the assassins before they can flee for reinforcements.
Azshara will fall!
QuestData.LogDescription: Use the Fresh Sponge to reveal and kill $1oa Zanj'ir Assassins.
